{"tid":543592,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] Monster Hunter World (16) 又死SER","createTime":"2018-01-28T15:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T16:34:16.000Z","uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08a94ca7b73888e19c8c04c4668532c07685675b","tid":543592,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://www.monsterhunterworld.com/images/share.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.monsterhunterworld.com%2Fimages%2Fshare.png&h=c727d2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資訊頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.capcom.com%2Fmanual%2FMHW%2Fzh-hant%2Fps4&d=9ZLfab60MJFe0WuPRHKg0Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=d7668d87\" target=\"_blank\">http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手Q&amp;A<br />\nQ : 玩咩武器好?<br />\nA : 覺得邊樣型就玩邊樣<br />\n<br />\nQ : 一開始用咩裝好?<br />\nA : 下位睇防禦力就可以 一係就飛雷龍<br />\n<br />\nQ : 多唔多人用 弓/笛/鎚/乜乜物物<br />\nA : 多<br />\n<br />\nQ : 咩武器高輸出<br />\nA : 用得勁, 咩武器都高輸出<br />\n<br />\nQ : 玩男角定女角?<br />\nA : 隨你<br />\n<br />\nQ : 咩武器高輸出<br />\nA : 用得勁, 咩武器都高輸出<br />\n<br />\nQ :有無人開個新手群？<br />\nA : 冇，有咩就係度講/係度約戰<br />\n<br />\nQ :點解連唔到線既?<br />\nA: 因為要俾錢買PS plus<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有冇pc版？幾時出？<br />\nA: 預計2018秋季出，除此之外咩情報都冇<br />\n<br />\nQ : 買左日英文版...係咪要買返中文版?<br />\nA : 睇說明啦文盲<br />\n<br />\nQ: 噴血少左點算好<br />\nA: 設定係咁<br />\n<br />\nQ: 傷害數字好撚核突可唔可以整走<br />\nA: Option有得較走<br />\n<br />\nQ: LOCK人有冇得用番3DS果款<br />\nA: Option有得set<br />\n<br />\nQ:買錯日英版點算?<br />\nA:屌你老母個老母<br />\n<br />\nQ: 大家同一進度點樣可以一齊clear/故事進度不足<br />\nA: 低進度入唔到高進度個任,4個人都要先觸發劇情 去到見到條龍 可以發出SOS訊號既位<br />\n之後quit任 再重開就可以一齊玩一齊clear<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">溫暖的毛皮</span></span>/翼龍皮打咩先有<br />\nA: 森林開地圖睇,打鹿<br />\n   用石仔或者遠攻打翼龍  <br />\n<br />\nQ. 順風護石係邊到拎<br />\nA. redeem完係房個貓<br />\n<br />\nQ.開左角色之後,可唔可以重設?改唔改到名?<br />\nA.骨架類嘅整唔到,名改唔到<br />\n<br />\nQ.Horizon 個任一開就解散<br />\nA.個任有bug<br />\n<br />\nQ: 深海結晶係邊度有?<br />\nA: 珊瑚map做礦工<br />\n<br />\nQ:輝龍石到底邊度有?<br />\nA: 熔山龍身上挖礦<br />\n<br />\nQ: 設罝地的營區喺邊?<br />\nA: 地圖右上方<br />\n<br />\nQ: 再開過個人,咁之前beta報酬同特典有冇得再拎過<br />\nA: 有巴打試過有<br />\n<br />\nQ: 買咩機好/機同game幾錢?<br />\nA: 請去報價區問<br />\n<br />\nQ:冇香港PSN 係咪要買多次?<br />\nA:唔需要,可以開個香港account set常用ps4<br />\n  就可以用有買嘅account玩<br />\n<br />\nQ: Q&amp;A冇我想要嘅答案<br />\nA: 建議先睇圖鑑,多謝合作<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有人講上位係咩黎<br />\nA: 上位=進階 進階=上位</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bdcbe9e631075299d73ae409cf430c8c09bb3eed","tid":543592,"uid":61133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 想玩先嚟死 你老母位老母個老母"},{"pid":"dc241849ae5da6a2de777697ee96d718f33afbb7","tid":543592,"uid":13281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdcbe9e631075299d73ae409cf430c8c09bb3eed","tid":543592,"uid":61133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 想玩先嚟死 你老母位老母個老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:15:14.000Z","msg":"我鬧埋你阿爸 鬧埋你阿爺 再鬧埋你阿爺既阿爺 鬧埋你祖宗十八代！！！！！"},{"pid":"2ecc47bc8d3b9d922e61b485ecd6840e8171fb3f","tid":543592,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:18:27.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"bc51ae63dffb81d421d6eb467a19ce877b490e5c","tid":543592,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩上左11HR, 有個任叫我調查痴火龍的??? 既任要點做, 接唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da09f65e0de0f7e73a02a194c19ab5dd9b18036","tid":543592,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"係咁死ser mon hun痴線多人玩"},{"pid":"a174d28a01fe98bd535ce84da885eaae86c0a07f","tid":543592,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc51ae63dffb81d421d6eb467a19ce877b490e5c","tid":543592,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":